      "value": {
        "latex": "On pose pour $(x,y)\\in\\R^2$~:\n$$f(x,y) = x^2+y^2-2x^2y - \\frac{4x^6y^2}{(x^4+y^2)^2}\\quad\\text{si }(x,y)\\ne 0,\n  \\qquad f(0,0)=0.$$",
        "html": "<p>On pose pour <span class=\"math inline\">\\((x,y)\\in\\R^2\\)</span> :\n<span class=\"math display\">\\[f(x,y) = x^2+y^2-2x^2y -\n\\frac{4x^6y^2}{(x^4+y^2)^2}\\quad\\text{si }(x,y)\\ne 0,\n  \\qquad f(0,0)=0.\\]</span></p>\n"
